  <title>Adjust the contrast</title>

  <p>You can adjust the contrast of windows and buttons so that they're easier
  to see. This is not the same as changing the brightness of the whole screen
  since only parts of the <gui>user interface</gui> will change.</p>

  <steps>
    <title>To adjust the contrast of your window:</title>
    <item>
      <p>Click on the <gui>User Menu</gui> on the bottom left-hand corner of
      your screen, then click on <gui>Settings</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click on <gui>Universal Access</gui> to open the panel.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Switch <gui>High Contrast</gui> to <gui>ON</gui>.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>
